data.description: SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED! This home is ready for new owners with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. NO flood insurance required. NEW roof with metal trusses, soffits and gutters completed a few months ago. Updated kitchen with Corian countertops along with new stainless-steel appliances, A/C, water heater and well pump have all been replaced in 2023. There is a 10x10 shed with LVP flooring and A/C in the backyard that can be used as a guest room, office or hobby room. NW Cape offers a quick commute to shopping, schools, area restaurants, and golf courses. Whether you are an investor or looking for a new home, schedule an appointment to see this adorable home and make an offer.
